            "language_code": "en",
            "text": "A'famosa Melaka"
          }
        ]
      },
      "description": {
        "localized_texts": [
          {
            "language_code": "en",
            "text": "A’Famosa Melaka is one of Malaysia’s most popular integrated resorts, offering a wide range of attractions suitable for families, couples, and groups. Located in Alor Gajah, Melaka, it combines theme parks, wildlife experiences, and leisure facilities in one destination.Visitors can enjoy thrilling water rides, exciting animal encounters, and relaxing resort surroundings, making it an ideal getaway for both short trips and extended stays."
          }
        ]
      },
      "rating": {
        "average_value": 4.3,
        "rating_count": 100
      },
      "product_features": [
        {
          "feature_type": "TEXT_FEATURE_HIGHLIGHT",
          "value": {
            "localized_texts": [
              {
                "language_code": "en",
                "text": "A’ Famosa Water Theme Park: One of the largest water parks in Malaysia, built among lush greeneries."
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "feature_type": "TEXT_FEATURE_HIGHLIGHT",
          "value": {
            "localized_texts": [
              {
                "language_code": "en",
                "text": "A’ Famosa Safari Wonderland: This safari wonderland is a place where you will be able to see and interact with wild and rare animals."
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "feature_type": "TEXT_FEATURE_HIGHLIGHT",
          "value": {
            "localized_texts": [
              {
                "language_code": "en",
                "text": "Big Ice Cream: One of the tallest, longest and widest ICE CREAM in Southeast Asia with its heights of 20.8 meter, the widest diameter length of 18.3 meter."
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "feature_type": "TEXT_FEATURE_HIGHLIGHT",
          "value": {
            "localized_texts": [
              {
                "language_code": "en",
                "text": "Wahaha / Hulala : Experience a  ride resembling a tsuname-like effect."
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "feature_type": "TEXT_FEATURE_INCLUSION",
          "value": {
            "localized_texts": [
              {
                "language_code": "en",
                "text": "Expect a full day of fun and leisure with a mix of thrilling rides, interactive experiences, and relaxing spaces. The park is designed for guests of all ages, with clearly marked zones, food outlets, rest areas, and amenities throughout the resort.Guests should be prepared for walking between areas and are encouraged to plan their visit according to the attraction operating hours. Some attractions may have height, age, or safety restrictions."
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "feature_type": "TEXT_FEATURE_MUST_KNOW",
          "value": {
            "localized_texts": [
              {
                "language_code": "en",
                "text": "Operation Hours: Please kindly visit A'Famosa Malacca official website for any updates of operation hours."
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "feature_type": "TEXT_FEATURE_MUST_KNOW",
          "value": {
            "localized_texts": [
              {
                "language_code": "en",
                "text": "Weather: In the event of severe weather conditions, it may become necessary to temporarily close the pools and attractions."
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "feature_type": "TEXT_FEATURE_MUST_KNOW",
          "value": {
            "localized_texts": [
              {
                "language_code": "en",
                "text": "Restrictions: For age, height or any restrictions for the slides in the park, please kindly visit A'Famosa Malacca official website for more information."
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        {
