            "localized_texts": [
              {
                "language_code": "en",
                "text": "Terms & Conditions: Admission Entry is permitted upon presentation of a valid voucher. Tickets are open-dated and valid on any operating day. Eligibility Safari & Water Theme Park: Children below 90 cm enjoy free admission. Fire Fly Digital Art Museum: Children below 3 years old enjoy free admission. All children must be accompanied by one (1) paying adult at all times. Attraction Access Admission is valid only for the attraction(s) stated on the ticket purchased. Attraction availability is subject to operational conditions. Additional Information This offer is not valid for Middle East & Iranian citizens. Guests from the above regions are required to purchase tickets directly at the counter. Important Notes Operating hours may vary and are subject to change without prior notice. Tickets are non-refundable and non-transferable."
